Package org.projecthusky.fhir.emed.ch.common

@DefaultQualifier(value=org.checkerframework.checker.nullness.qual.NonNull.class, locations={PARAMETER,RETURN,FIELD}) package org.projecthusky.fhir.emed.ch.common
The generic package for Swiss FHIR Implementation Guides.

By default, parameters and return values are annotated with NonNull except for the generated package. Nullable values are specifically annotated with Nullable.

Author:
Quentin Ligier
